1
00:00:07,930 --> 00:00:10,640
I love it when Princess Celestia
comes to Ponyville!

2
00:00:10,790 --> 00:00:13,400
I got my hooves shined
just like Rarity for the occasion.

3
00:00:13,550 --> 00:00:16,410
- Ya like?
- I certainly do!

4
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:18,750
I'm surprised she's not here yet.

5
00:00:18,900 --> 00:00:20,580
I wonder what's taking so long?

6
00:00:20,730 --> 00:00:22,500
And where are
Applejack and Fluttershy?

7
00:00:22,650 --> 00:00:26,300
Fluttershy's detained helping Applejack
with a mishap at Sweet Apple Acres.

8
00:00:26,450 --> 00:00:27,380
They'll be along.

9
00:00:27,530 --> 00:00:30,160
I still don't get why
the Princess would be so late.

10
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:32,270
She's bringing
an important visitor.

11
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:33,710
That could be part of it.

12
00:00:33,860 --> 00:00:36,450
A visitor who's important and slow.

13
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:39,430
Maybe it's somepony
so terribly important,

14
00:00:39,580 --> 00:00:42,600
she still had many more terribly important
things to do before she got here.

15
00:00:43,890 --> 00:00:47,900
Maybe the visitor has a deer antler,
a goat leg, a bat wing, and a snake tail!

16
00:00:48,370 --> 00:00:50,200
Yeah, right. That's Discord.

17
00:00:50,350 --> 00:00:52,000
Why in the
wide-wide world of Equestria

18
00:00:52,150 --> 00:00:54,820
would Princess Celestia
bring along someone like that?

19
00:00:54,970 --> 00:00:57,320
Maybe you should ask her!

